    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014it's been pampered since day one and looks just as good as the day I bought it. It drives like an absolute dream and is spotless inside and out. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will appreciate it just as much. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t find another one this clean!",
