    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving 4.0L S65 naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is in showroom condition, exhibiting factory-original paint depth and a pristine interior free of bolster wear. Mechanically, the individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized, delivering instantaneous throttle response up to the 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral grip and corner-exit traction. Rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively, ensuring this remains a turn-key example for the most demanding purist. No track time, no modifications, just pure mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
