      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in a condition that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, having been strictly garage-kept and exclusively hand-washed under my ownership. Inside, the cabin retains that signature new-car scent; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history detailing meticulous preventative maintenance that ensures a driving experience as smooth as it is powerful. From the pristine, dust-free engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It is a collector-grade example ready for its next discerning owner.",
      "price": 43900.0,
